> A reply to another post regarding melee Ranger vs Assassin:<br>
<br>
===========================================<br>
<br>
ealaniel: <br>
<br>
As you pointed out ealaniel, Evade and Absorption alone shows that Nightshades receive 14% less damage. <br>
<br>
DEFENSE: <br>
<br>
- Nightshades receive 14% less damage through Evasion vs Ranger Absorbtion. <br>
<br>
+? Ranger Qui Buff add to Evade? <br>
+ Ranger Self AF Buff <br>
+ Ranger Dex Buff increases Defense <br>
<br>
* The Quickness affecting Evade wasn't included in the original example because it has not been verified, but I seem to evade more often with a Dex/Qui buff from a Druid vs a regular Dex Buff. When I ran tests when I was around level 32, a combination of both Dex and Dex/Qui druid buffs from a full specialized Nurture Druid decreased damage from 80 to 60. Combine that with the Ranger Self AF Buff and that should overcome the base 14% advantage that the Nightshade has. <br>
<br>
OFFENSE: <br>
<br>
+ Rangers Attack Faster with Qui Buff. <br>
+ Rangers Receive Damage bonus from Str Buff. <br>
+ Rangers Receive Damage bonus from Dex Buff. <br>
<br>
- Cannot supplement a one time DoT or Debuff <br>
(38 damage tick x 5 = 190 damage over 20 seconds) <br>
<br>
+ Rangers do get a (9.4 DPS) damage add buff. Over the course of 5 seconds, that adds up to 47 damage (235 damage over 20 seconds), compared to the 38 damage DoT. That alone over the course is enough to do more damage over time than the Poison Dot. Rangers can miss, but Nightshades can both miss landing the poison and have it resisted completely. <br>
<br>
* The Ranger Damage Add alone defeats poison (so much for Envenom). The rest of the buffs add to damage as well. <br>
<br>
<br>
&gt;&quot;True, but to what extent. Anyone with level 12 bow skill actually tried to shoot anything level 50? I'm thinking that this may not work as well as you think.&quot; <br>
<br>
I never meant to say it works well, this is a Melee Ranger afterall. It was to show that the Melee Ranger has superior Melee and has an extra tool at Range still superior than what an Assassin can ever accomplish. <br>
<br>
The point of showing the autotrain in bows is not to suggest they are powerful, but to show Archers still have some kind of bow ability (albiet weaker) that is superior to anything an Assassin can accomplish, where the reverse can't be said if an Assassin wanted to specialize in range attack and still be better than the Archer at Melee. <br>
<br>
<br>
&gt;&gt;&quot;To actually *prove* that assassins were gimped vs melee archers you'd need to do an actual *test* for that, something that Ela has never bothered to do.&quot; <br>
<br>
If you can find an Assassin with that setup at level 50 and a Melee Hunter/Ranger of level 50 and they're not in the same realm, I would be glad to see a test set up. It's not something that I can be &quot;bothered&quot; to do, I can't whip up a level 50 melee Archer in another realm to test it out with a flick of my finger, but Mythic can. I'm a gamer that has to follow the rules, I can't set up something like that out of the blue, that's why I'd request it on Pendragon.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uvalarauco.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Valarauco</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/1/02 9:22:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1983.topic&index=21>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.attbi.com/~bdemong/valaface.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Ela’s Assassin Volume IV 1/2</span><hr size=1> Nothing has gone over my head, please read my two posts again, particularly the second. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uvalarauco.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Valarauco</A> at: 2/1/02 9:23:28 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ugeliel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>geliel </A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/1/02 11:58:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1983.topic&index=22>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.earthlink.net/~jwlibhart/_uimages/gelly85.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Ela’s Assassin Volume IV 1/2</span><hr size=1> This is a joke right?  I mean you aren't serio